{"tid":1947052,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有做依啲事既人 唔配叫自己做藍絲","createTime":"2020-03-28T04:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T07:12:22.000Z","uid":61520,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd1f8aeb0d191866d3f66f6fd0d2ebb10f54241","tid":1947052,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"- 用iphone (屌，買佢一部手機，一半錢送左俾美帝用來對付中国共產黨）<br />\n<br />\n- 用 android 手機（ google 出既系統，又係美帝產物，又間接送自己資料俾美帝）<br />\n<br />\n咁你會話，即係叫我地藍絲唔駛用手機啫<br />\n咁你係咪愛国愛黨，愛既就唔好用<br />\n好撚睇唔過班偽藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有咩唔做得既，諗到再講<br />\n各位藍絲同道都可以俾意見<br />\n大家為藍絲定一個準則， 咪俾啲人扮藍"},{"pid":"29aa8b4daad385717f74fba52951ef55d90ff218","tid":1947052,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"一定要用華為<br />\n<br />\n小米都唔可以<br />\n因為小米唔肯讓路俾華為上"},{"pid":"2aa2e65d2fcb49ee7db658da125ead3665207807","tid":1947052,"uid":61520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"29aa8b4daad385717f74fba52951ef55d90ff218","tid":1947052,"uid":82640,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"一定要用華為<br />\n<br />\n小米都唔可以<br />\n因為小米唔肯讓路俾華為上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"華為都用android 啦， 點用得落手"},{"pid":"a807f62ec7b3e652a94d4b23818463fe96b4082f","tid":1947052,"uid":47041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"一定唔開可以戴口罩<br />\n好人好姐無病戴乜撚<br />\n我地英雄兒女中左招都唔會戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2810f8b26f3c36f793d5ca1cca6146ba422ce5","tid":1947052,"uid":20442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"睇大公報，文匯報；唔應該用FB，用微信；<br />\n<br />\n中產藍絲仔女都係英美讀書，超級奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj